   <style>
    /*-------- Structure Styles  --------*/
             
             .main {
                 max-width: 1170px;
                 min-height: 500px;
                 margin: 0 auto;
             }
             
             .main-wrapper {
                 padding-top: 30px;
             }              
             
             .lead-stories {
                 display: flex;
             }
             
             .lead-stories > div {
                 flex: 1 0 auto;
                 width: 25%;
             }
             
             /*-------- Story --------*/
             
             .story {
                 padding: 30px;
             }
             
             .story h3:after {
                 background: none;
                 margin-top: 0;
             }
             
             .story a:hover {
                 text-decoration: underline;
             }
             
             .story img {
                 width: 100%;
                 height: auto;
             }
             
             	   .story .story-btn {
                 background: transparent;
                 border: 1px solid #9f1c2b;
                 padding: 0.5rem;
                 width: 120px; 
                 height: 40px;
                 background-size: 100% 200%;
                 background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 50%, #9f1c2b 50%);
                 -webkit-transition: background-position .2s;
                 -moz-transition: background-position .2s;
                 transition: background-position .2s;
                 color: #000;
             }
             
             .story .story-btn:hover, .story .story-btn:hover > a {
                 background-position: 0 -100%;
                 color: #fff;                
             }            
             
             .story > .story-btn {
                 text-decoration: none;
                 color: #9f1c2b;
                 border: 1px solid #9f1c2b;
                 padding: 10px 15px;
                 font-size: 13px;
             }
             
             .story > .story-btn:hover {
                 text-decoration: none;
             }    
 
             /*END OF STYLE UPDATES*/
             
             .story-header {
                 margin-top: 15px;
                 margin-bottom: 5px;
                 line-height: 2rem; 
                 font-weight: 700;
                 font-weight: normal;
             }
             
             .story-header > a {
                 font-size: 1.5rem;
                 line-height: 1rem;
                 font-weight: normal;
                 text-decoration: none;
                 color: #000;
             }
             
             .story-header > a:hover {
                 text-decoration: none;
             }
             
             /*-------- Story Details --------*/
             
             .story-details {
                 border-top: 1px dotted #c41230;
                 border-bottom: 1px solid #b3b3b1;
                 padding-top: 10px;
                 padding-bottom: 10px;
                 margin-bottom: 20px;
             }
             
             .story-details a {
                 color: #c41230;
                 font-weight: bold;
                 text-decoration: none;
             }
             
             .story-details p {
                 font-size: 1rem;
                 margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
             }    
             
             @media (max-width: 767px){
                 .lead-stories {
                     /*flex-direction: column;*/
                     display: block;
                 }
                 
                 .lead-stories > div {
                     width: 100%;
                 }
                 
                 .story-header > a {
                     font-size: 1.5rem;
                 }
             } 
             
             /*-------- Videos --------*/
             
             .videos {
                 padding: 20px;
                 padding-top: 0;
             }
             
             .videos h3 {
                 font-size: 1.7rem;
                 margin: 0;
             }
             
             .videos h3:after {
                 content: none;
             }
             
             .video-wrapper {
                 background-color: #000;
                 display: flex;
                 flex-wrap: wrap;
             }
             
             .video-wrapper p {
                 color: #fff;
                 font-size: .8rem;
             }
             
             .video-wrapper > div {
                 flex: 1 0 auto;
                 width: 20%;
             }
             
             .video-inner {
                 padding: 20px;
             }
             
             .video-inner p {
                 margin-bottom: 0;
             }
             
             
             @media (max-width: 767px){
                 .video-wrapper {
                     padding: 0;
                     display: block;
                 }
                 
                 .video-wrapper p {
                     display: none;
                 }
                 
                 .video-wrapper > div {
                     display: block;
                     width: 100%;
                 }      
                 
                 .video-inner {
                     width: 50%;
                     margin: 0 auto;
                 }
             }
             
             @media (max-width: 640px){ 
                 .video-inner {
                     width: 60%;
                     margin: 0 auto;
                     padding: 0;
                 }
             }
             
             @media (max-width: 340px){ 
                 .video-inner {
                     width: 80%;
                     padding: 0;
                 }
             }
             
             /*-------- News --------*/
             
             .news {
                padding: 20px; 
                padding-bottom: 40px; 
             }
             
             .news-wrapper {
                 display: flex;
             }
             
             .news-wrapper:nth-of-type(1n+2) {
                 margin-top: 20px;
             }
             
             .news-item {
                 flex: 0 0 auto;
                 width: 32%;
                 border: 1px solid #b1b1b1;
                 background-color: #fff;
             }
             
             .news-item:nth-of-type(1n+2) {
                 margin-left: 20px;
             }
             
             .news-item > div {
                 padding: 20px;
             }  
             
             .news-item .news-headline {
                 padding-top: 0;
                 padding-bottom: 0;
                 border-bottom: 1px dotted #c41230;
             }
             
             .news-item .news-headline h4 {
                 margin-top: 1rem;
                 margin-bottom: 1rem;
                 font-size: 1.1rem;
                 line-height: 1.4rem;
                 font-weight: bold;
             }
             
             .news-item .news-body p {
                 font-size: 1rem;
             }
             
             .news-item .news-body p:first-child {
                 margin-top: 0;
             }
             
             .news-item .news-body a {
                 color: #c41230;
                 text-decoration: none;
                 font-size: 1rem;
             }
             
             .news-item .news-body a.call-to-action {
                 display: block;
                 font-size: .9rem;
             }
             
             .news-item .news-body a:hover {
                 text-decoration: underline;
             }      
             
             @media (max-width: 768px){
                 .news-wrapper {
                     display: block;
                 }
                 
                 .news-item {
                     display: block;
                     width: 100%;
                     margin-bottom: 30px;
                 }
                 
                 .news-item:nth-of-type(1n+2) {
                     margin-left: 0;
                 }
                 
                 .news-item > img {
                     width: 100%;
                     height: auto;
                 }
                h3.cim2 { 
 display: none;
 }
             }

            <div class="news-body">
             <p>
              Whether you’re a company rewarding hard work, or a bunch of friends that want to get out of the house, you can’t beat a great night of theater at The Rep! Groups are available for 10 or more people with discounts starting at 15% off and up. Plus Groups get to pick seats before shows go on sale to the general public.

            </a>
            <div class="news-headline">
             <h4>
              Casting Announced for
              <br/>
              Fall Productions at The Rep!
             </h4>
            </div>
            <div class="news-body">
             <p>
              <span>
               Kicking off the season is
               <em>
                Songs for Nobodies
               </em>
               featuring Milwaukee Rep favorite
               <strong>
                Bethany Thomas
               </strong>
               in this one-woman tour-de-force production.
               <em>
                Guards at the Taj
               </em>
               brings back to The Rep
               <strong>
                Owais Ahmen
               </strong>
               previously seen in Ayad Akhtar’s
               <em>
                The Invisible Hand
               </em>
               .
               <em>
                The All Night Strut!
               </em>
               will feature
               <strong>
                Kelley Faulkner
               </strong>
               and we’ve found our Mary for
               <em>
                Miss Bennet: Christmas at Pemberley
               </em>
               -
               <strong>
                Rebecca Hurd
               </strong>
               .
               <strong>
               </strong>
               Read the release below to see who else has been cast
              </span>
              <span>
               .
              </span>
             </p>

              <a class="call-to-action" href="/RepGlobal/1617img/pr-20180712.pdf">

             <h4>
              Be Part Of The Great
              <br/>
              American Read This Summer!
             </h4>

            <div class="news-body">
             <p>
              Join the Great American Read and revisit the classic novel
              <em>
               Pride and Prejudice
              </em>

              <em>
               <a href="/Tickets--Events/201819-Season/Miss-Bennet-Christmas-at-Pemberley/">
                Miss Bennet: Christmas at Pemberley
               </a>
              </em>
              , this November at The Rep.
              <span>
               Once you’ve read the book, answer our trivia question to unlock

              the promo code to save on ticket prices to
              <em>
               Miss Bennet
              </em>
              . But hurry the offer is only valid until Sept. 30.

              <br/>

            </div>
            <div class="news-body">
             <p>
              Join us for a free play reading of a piece under development as part of The Rep’s John (Jack) D. Lewis NPDP program. Presented by The Rep and the United Community Center
              <em>
               Grandma’s Empanadas
              </em>
              is a play exploring a community’s heritage and identity through music, food, and personal narratives. This play is based entirely on interviews with Milwaukee’s Latin community.

              <br/>
              United Community Center
